NB:Run this with Python 2. Some of the modules have problems working in Python 3
Make sure the VizScript.py file is in the same directory as the zip file
After you navigate to the directory containing the VizScript.py and zip file, pass VizScript.py
as the first argument and the zip file you want to visualize as the second argument and run

This script is currently a prototype and has one or two things that need to be ironed out to acheive desired outcome
